snippet.title: These Nikola Tesla Quotes Are Life Changing
snippet.description:
These Nikola Tesla Quotes Are Life Changing. Life changing quotes and thoughts by Nikola Tesla.

These are vivid sayings and quotes from Nikola Tesla. The best quotes and aphorisms of Nikola Tesla that will make you think about many things in life. Life quotes from Nikola Tesla are definitely worth your time.

Nikola Tesla was a Serbian-American inventor, electrical engineer, mechanical engineer, and futurist best known for his contributions to the design of the modern alternating current electricity supply system.
